				<code>{% raw %}{{ out.getSectionName }}{% endraw %}</code>
			
				<pre class="prettyprint">about_us</pre>
			</td>
		</tr>
		
		
		<tr>
			<th>link2(article, isSection, tags)</th>
			<td><strong>article</strong>: (string) Returns relative link string article (<code>article</code> is articles textual ID) or to site homepage (if <code>article</code> is home), depending on current url<br />
				<strong>isSection</strong>: (boolean) If true It's a link to a section blog. Default: false<br />
				<strong>tags</strong>: (array): tags used to filter section blog. Default: false
